                <div class="price">0&euro; <span>/ mois</span></div>
                <div class="price-desc">Pour d&eacute;couvrir l'application</div>
                <div style="display:inline-block;padding:0.25rem 0.75rem;background:rgba(74,144,217,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(74,144,217,0.2);border-radius:50px;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:1.5rem">7 jours de Pro offerts &agrave; l'inscription</div>
                <ul class="pricing-features">
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Enregistrement des s&eacute;ances</li>
