                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Plans d'entra&icirc;nement (jusqu'&agrave; 12 semaines)</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Cr&eacute;ation de groupes &amp; d&eacute;fis</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Analyses avanc&eacute;es</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Analyse de surentra&icirc;nement</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Support prioritaire</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/login/" class="btn-pricing primary">S'abonner &agrave; Pro</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Comparison Table -->
    <section class="comparison-section">
        <h2>Comparaison d&eacute;taill&eacute;e</h2>
        <div class="comparison-table-wrapper">
        <table class="comparison-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Fonctionnalit&eacute;</th><th>Gratuit (+ essai 7j)</th><th>Pro</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr><td>Enregistrement des s&eacute;ances</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Suivi de progression basique</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Acc&egrave;s communaut&eacute;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
